org.eclipse.jst.ws.jaxws.dom.runtime.persistence
Interface IProjectSelector

public interface IProjectSelector

Specifies what java projects will be traversed by a given ICompilationUnitFinder instance. If any of the registered selectors approved the project i.e. IProjectSelector.approve(IJavaProject) returned true, then this project will be traversed. I.e. the project needs to be rejected by all the selectors in order not to be traversed. An implementation of this interface should reject a project that it has no knowledge about.

Author:
Hristo Sabev
